{"tid":781421,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"後腰右側痛應該睇骨醫/脊醫/物理治療？","createTime":"2018-08-16T01:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T05:05:06.000Z","uid":14436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e80619387c2c2f652c93d366fdb53477624484df","tid":781421,"uid":14436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:27:19.000Z","msg":"上個月做完gym後發覺後腰右邊只要一受壓（e.g個人後右後咁挨）就會痛，連帶有少少腳痛，情況都持續一個月<br />\n<br />\n上兩個星期睇左普通西醫，佢有開d藥但食左情況都無改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我問佢跟住再痛應該睇邊科醫生佢又話食完藥應該會無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGoogle過一輪之後我懷疑自己係椎間盤突出，想問巴打如果呢個情況我應該去睇骨醫/脊醫/物理治療？<br />\n或者例如我去睇骨科先，佢會再refer我？<br />\n<br />\nThx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3c825fbe6926fe9d18903066dc12dc9d021f04","tid":781421,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:30:11.000Z","msg":"急症180 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過非緊急預等幾粒鐘"},{"pid":"11278307154c1828e321be84de0a5423d203f212","tid":781421,"uid":188540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6c3c825fbe6926fe9d18903066dc12dc9d021f04","tid":781421,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:30:11.000Z","msg":"急症180 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過非緊急預等幾粒鐘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T01:31:53.000Z","msg":"行得走得睇急症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b9c1dd85e051b0c84dd8a41133de06634a4ad8","tid":781421,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11278307154c1828e321be84de0a5423d203f212","tid":781421,"uid":188540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6c3c825fbe6926fe9d1890306